    "Across various models, including OPT 1.3B, Llama 2 and Vicuna 33B, our approach consistently outperformed baseline methods.",
    "The trend observed was similar to that seen in the ComVE dataset: While larger models like Llama 2 (70B) and Vicuna 33B performed strongly, the most significant performance boost was observed in smaller models such as OPT 1.3B.",
    "This suggests that our TIP framework is particularly effective in enhancing the reasoning capabilities of smaller models while still offering improvements for larger models that already possess considerable inherent reasoning power.",
    "In summary, our experimental The best results in each setting are highlighted in bold and italics, while the second-best is underlined results across both datasets substantiate the effectiveness of the TIP framework in enhancing the commonsense reasoning abilities of LLMs.",
    "The framework consistently delivers superior performance in generating accurate, contextually appropriate explanations, thereby advancing the performance of LLMs in commonsense explanation generation."
